# HTML and CSS Patterns

## HTML Structure
- Use `<!DOCTYPE html>` and proper HTML5 structure
- Set `lang="id"` for Indonesian language
- Use UTF-8 charset: `<meta charset="UTF-8">`
- Include Font Awesome for icons: `https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css`

## CSS Styling Patterns
- Use 'Segoe UI' as primary font family
- Color scheme: Purple gradient (#8c52ff to #34c5cb) for headers
- Background colors: #FDFBFF for body, #f2eaff for containers
- Border radius: 25px for buttons, 30px for containers
- Box shadows: `0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)` for cards

## Button Styling
```css
.button {
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background-color: #EBD6FB;
    color: #4b3e58;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: bold;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
}
```

## Table Styling
- Use `border-collapse: collapse` for clean tables
- Consistent padding: 8px for cells
- Border: 1px solid #999

## Responsive Design
- Use `@media(max-width: 768px)` for mobile responsiveness
- Flexbox for layout: `display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;`
- Mobile-first approach with `flex-direction: column` on small screens

## Form Styling
- Input groups with icons using absolute positioning
- Rounded inputs with 25px border-radius
- Purple theme: #8e2de2 for primary buttons
- Real-time validation with visual feedback
- Status indicators for field validation
